overviewContent.value: Quadrilaterals are shapes with four sides. This one changes as you play with its connected corners and sides. Moving a corner or side changes your shape in different ways all at once. You cannot break your shape or make sides or corners cross over. Use shape markers, background grid, and diagonal guides as needed to create different shapes in the quadrilateral family. You can show shape name, mute shape sounds, quickly reset shape or start over with reset all.
